item.title: Report X-2023070742
item.description:
Report X-2023070742

Identified by scraper @ 2023-08-16T06:13:42+00:00

  • Incident Date: 2023-07-03
  • City: LENEXA
  • State: KS
  • Report Type: A hazardous material incident
  • Mode Of Transportation: Highway
  • Carrier/Reporter: Fedex Ground Package System, Inc.
  • Hazmat Fatalities: 0
  • Hazmat Injuries: 0
  • Non-Hazmat Fatalities: 0
  • Description: SequenceEvent: A PACKAGE HANDLER NOTICED THIS PACKAGE WAS LEAKING AND REPORTED IT TO QA. QA RUSHED OVER TO THE TABLE AND NOTICED IT WAS HAZARDOUS AND CLEANED OFF THE AREA WITH ZZAMPHO AND LOOSE ABSORB. ONCE THE AREA WAS CLEANED, THEY BROUGHT THE PACKAGE BACK TO QA AND PLACED IN THE HAZMAT PROCESSING CAGE. DescribePack: THE PACKAGE WAS LOADED ONTO ITS SIDE AND CAUSED THE LID TO THE PAIL TO COME LOOSE. DurationRel: 1 and MitigateEffect: THE PACKAGE WAS PLACED IN A TOTE WITH A LINED HAZMAT BAG AND CLEANED UP WITH ZZAMPHO AND LOOSE ABSORB.

  • Description: SequenceEvent: WHILE QA WAS DOING A WALK, THEY NOTICED THIS PACKAGE WAS LEAKING AND PLACED IT IN A TOTE WITH A LINED HAZMAT BAG. THEY BROUGHT THE PACKAGE BACK TO QA AND PLACED IN THE HAZMAT CAGE BECAUSE THEY NOTICED THE STRONG AROMA FROM THE PACKAGE BUT DID NOT SEE ANY LABELS ON THE OUTSIDE OTHER THAN THE BARCODE. DescribePack: ONE OF THE BOTTLES IS PUNCTURED ON THE BOTTOM SIDE AND CAUSED THE CONTENTS TO LEAK OUT. DurationRel: 3 and MitigateEffect: THE PACKAGE WAS PLACED IN A TOTE WITH A LINED HAZMAT BAG AND PLACED IN THE HAZMAT PROCESSING CAGE.

  • Description: UNLOAD SUPERVISOR RADIOED INTO DMP WITH A HAZMAT LEAKER. DMP DISPATCHED A RESPONDER TO THE LEAKER WITH FULL PPE AND FULLY STOCKED SPILL CART. RESPONDER ARRIVED AND CONSULTED THE DECISON TREE TO FIND THE APPROIATE RESPONES STEPS. FOLLOWING THE DECISION TREE, THE RESPONDER CLEANED UP THE SPILL AND BROUGHT THE LEAKER BACK TO DMP FOR PROPER DISPOSAL OF THE HAZMAT.

  • Description: SequenceEvent: Package was found leaking outside of a trailer and the load side manager gave this package to QA. QA then took this package to the Hazmat cage for processing. QA took cleaning supplies over to the cleanup and got everything cleaned up. DescribePack: Package failed due to one of the bottles being open or not on all the way. DurationRel: 1 and MitigateEffect: QA took this package to the hazmat cage and got it off the dock. QA also put down absorbable pads to soak up anything left behind.
